Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.10,0:00:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.49,0:00:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.70,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that in three years we'd \Nbe good enough to do mainstream.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you weren't planning \Non getting our cult manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Money and Intelligence," serialized \Nin the first place, were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then we \Nwant to do mainstream now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that you're more likely to make \Nit big with something that isn't mainstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we want to do mainstream.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is the genius type.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.83,0:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do a mainstream\Nmanga, you can't beat him.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.22,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of us here in the editing \Ndepartment don't think even Niizuma
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,can become number one in Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say there's no \Nway we can beat Niizuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.16,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mainstream manga has never \Nbeen published alongside his.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell just by looking at your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're really saying is that {\i1}this{\i2} \Nname has no chance of beating him, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.07,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have six months!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.08,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't convince me by then, you \Ntwo will listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.50,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you still insist on doing mainstream \Nafter that, then I'll step down as your editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.63,0:01:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:16.93,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you see the blue bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:16.93,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,aozora tobikau Blue Bird
