Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainstream, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I don't think there's any room \Nin Jack for more mainstream right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, with a mainstream manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.35,0:02:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really know if it's any \Ngood until you see the actual votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, this name is no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you right now that even in \NNext, this wouldn't make it to the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, there's nothing original about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.01,0:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of new writers who bring \Nin names that take pieces from past hits,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing that'll become a hit itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori really does know his stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.34,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the mainstream battle \Nmanga that newcomers bring in
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has a lot of the same elements.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The important things are:
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple, easy-to-understand setting.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.64,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A clearly stated reason why the main character \Nis fighting that the reader can relate to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.80,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense battle scenes with \Nclean, easy to follow composition.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.11,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy characters with either a similar battle strength \Nas the protagonist or some sort of interesting ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always good to throw in a \Ncute heroine too, if possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.70,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Add a bit of humor and some tear-jerker \Nscenes, and you would have a strong story.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.80,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving us so much advice even though we're \Ngoing against your recommendations—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.84,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that you guys aren't \Nsuited to writing mainstream manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.14,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling you the basics of what\Nmakes a good mainstream manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I said tear-jerker scenes will \Nmake a strong story, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The readers have a good eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are trying too hard, \Nthey will see right through you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying it'll just fall flat instead?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, you can't force the story—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, how should I put it—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write without thinking about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided to go with Crow for serialization,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so I told them I wanted to head home \Nafter saying goodbye to Ashirogi-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.82,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Why's he acting so friendly towards us?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.43,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, what do you mean \Nby write without thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think up a name first.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though everybody else \Nshould feel the same way,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,all the editors keep going on and \Non about them. I think it's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.24,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They made me write a name for \N"Yellow Hit," but it wasn't any fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.20,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure drew those names quickly a minute ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.00,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You drew 25 pages for chapter two and 23 \Npages for chapter three in under 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you did already have them \Nplanned out in your head, that's fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was a lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't even thought about them yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because I figured they\Nwouldn't let me serialize Crow
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if I told them I didn't have anything planned out.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How were you able to do all that so \Nquickly with nothing thought out?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The characters have a life of their own!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.28,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help them move and see what they \Nwill do next so much that I just can't stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the same way?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.80,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Characters coming to life and moving on their own—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what manga is to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing at all like these two.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't help them at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Movement!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.59,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.59,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.91,0:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that you enjoy drawing so much,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's normal to start with a name.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you make all your decisions.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.99,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't draw \Nsomething you haven't thought of,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so I probably think about \Nsomething before I draw it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured out how we \Nshould draw our manga now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I see your next manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about that,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're going to get serialized
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and catch up to you as soon as we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both give it our best.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure that your series continues
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and wait for us to get serialized as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might already be number \None by then, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should be so naive
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as to think you'll become number one that easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.55,0:07:30.17,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I have no money, so \Ncould you take me home by taxi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji and those two.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manipulating us adults like that—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have made them \Ntake this home with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.07,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.31,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,There's something else in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.20,0:07:48.65,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.27,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He brought in a character sketch, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.04,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,There sure is a lot of feeling in this drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.50,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's like you can see the \Npassion in everything they do.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.62,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even so, what makes or breaks a battle \Nmanga is how well you can draw movement.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, I wouldn't have thought you would \Nbe the kind to like "Money and Intelligence."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought it was really good.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.56,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like Ashirogi-sensei \Nis going to do a battle manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Those two?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really imagine that—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, I don't think they'll \Nbe able to do it well.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Ashirogi-sensei will \Nbecome my biggest rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the little one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd climb his way up even if he was on his own.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sorry. I have no idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought those assistants \Nover earlier today, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes were completely different then theirs.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they were calm, but \Nwith an inner intensity like fire.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the eyes of the hero of a battle manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.84,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What's with this kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.37,0:08:56.22,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is this the way manga geniuses see things?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, wait! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori was talking about it before.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.93,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is the genius type that'll get a \Nhit just by writing whatever he wants to.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The type that'll become a huge hit \Nwithout even trying are those just like Eiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You said before that you figured \Nout how we should draw our manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.24,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's more like—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just gone back to square one.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainstream or whatever, there \Nare two ways to go about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Either have the characters \Ndraw themselves like Eiji does,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.13,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or be calculating in a way that doesn't \Nmake it look like we're being calculating.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds complicated.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A reason to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.99,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of obvious things that we \Nnever really thought about it up until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we include everything Hattori mentioned, \Nwe can come up with something amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.64,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who has to write a calculated \Nstory that doesn't look calculated, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like writing it without \Nthinking would be better, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.41,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man! Mainstream really is a lot harder to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll help out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But in any case, our real battle starts now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sounds like the line out of \Nthe last chapter of some manga.
