Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(406.667,591.639)\b0\blur0.869\fnHelvetica Neue\fs50.139\c&H727672&}Crazy Prince
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't good enough, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.93,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to keep going if you get \Nso down every time you fail an audition.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do your best next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go change, then we can go.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:41.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(473.333,167.13)\fnArial\frz-16\fax-0.28\b1\fs26.741\blur0.869\c&HCEBEEC&}St. Visual's\NGirls Academy
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a late night anime starting this summer \Ncalled "St. Visual's Girls Academy."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try out for the role of a student?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're asking all the offices \Nfor recommended new-comers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they want someone with \Ngood acting and some singing ability, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes please!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.92,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Good acting. Singing ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The audition is the Sunday after next.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The particulars are all in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
