Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachioji was pretty far, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It kinda \Nfeels like I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H—Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you change?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we promised to show \Neach other our school uniforms.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I went home and then went \Nto my training school first.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I went in my uniform, I'd stand out too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, how was your last audition?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.60,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it again? That one \Nabout the stuck up princess—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! So this is your new place?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even bigger than before.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W—What is?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're starting to look so grown-up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take your stuff upstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo! How've you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Better be careful, grown-up-looking Miyoshi,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or you'll wrinkle your uniform.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I still act about Mina-chan's age, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"St. Visual's Girls Academy."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,394.426)\fscx95\fnArial\frz-3.5\fax0.35\b1\fs33.426\blur0.869\c&HC3B1E5&}St. Visual's\N\hGirls Academy
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, that's for an audition I have coming up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Audition?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm terribly sorry! My legs are just SO long.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! What's this doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's on earth could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet stuff like that happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an all girl school, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah it does!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds of a feather flock together, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.69,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're using that wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that you got another audition.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:25.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh~ how the seasons change.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.84,0:14:33.10,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Forever waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.81,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,For a brilliant dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, I'm leaving your towel here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.93,0:15:16.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh~ how the seasons change.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's okay for me to audition.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how are things going with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.36,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you kissed yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.57,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, we haven't really \Nbeen able to go on many dates.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi's been really busy lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really want to see him do well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.46,0:15:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi and his partner Mashiro\Nare both working really hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to write a battle manga,\NTakagi even had me beat him up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mashiro is copying hundreds\Nof drawings for practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're giving it all they've got
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and not complaining about how hard it is at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to do the audition?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been yourself all day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.89,0:16:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, you can just say so, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If they give you any trouble, I'll just beat 'em up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not very good yet
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have no confidence in my singing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.68,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if it's even okay that I audition.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm gonna try.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try harder like Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
