Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! I guess I was just nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.86,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanba Kana, you're up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, please state your agency and name.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Eight. Azuki Miho.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for seeing me today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You come up with anything good?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something funny and tear-jerking—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just planning out something funny is hard enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if it flows naturally with the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Flows naturally, huh—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.88,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda scary to think that Eiji \Nwrote that chapter of Crow for Next
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,without doing a name first.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad we got to meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.25,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm more determined than ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.47,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing that even after a \Nyear we can still get fired up like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A year?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a year since I asked \Nyou to pair up with me and write manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it has.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the day before midterms, wasn't it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Time sure flies, but that's life.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head over to the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,R—Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to write a \Ngood mainstream manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll ever figure out \Nthe tricks to doing this smoothly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole year, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we say we want to get \Nan anime by the time we're 18—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.18,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.89,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
