Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:12.89,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.003\b1\c&H4B4546&\move(678.667,834.311,566.667,377.044)\fs26.741\frz14.7\fax0.02}I got a part as a girl named Saotomeji Reika\Nin an anime called "St. Visual's Girls Academy."\NIt's only a small one, but I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki got her debut role.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I can read it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she really did!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That series running in {\i2}Young Three{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a pretty small role, but that's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki really got a role as a voice actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we already had our debut in Next.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.46,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That means both of you are a little \Nbit closer to your dreams, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.68,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about voice acting,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you become popular \Na lot faster than with a manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she starts showing up on TV,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll probably get popular really fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she is especially cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried, just ask \Nher to stay out of the media.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I can't ask her to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you texting for, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to say 'Congratulations'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.62,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.003\b1\pos(313.333,635.093)\fs40.111\frz14.7\fax-0.01\c&H575554&}Congratulations! Even if you get a role as a heroine, \Nplease wait for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Send!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This really makes me impatient, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as fast as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.81,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,645)\blur1.337\c&H33272F&\pos(403.333,200.556)\fs66.852\frz14.8\fax-0.03}Dummy!
