Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:39.82,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(651,1300)\blur1.003\b1\c&H6E6A6F&\move(829.333,800.217,690.667,223.954)\fs26.741\frz14.7\fax-0.02}Mashiro, you dummy! *lol*\NThat doesn't sound like you at all!
