Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.45,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.52,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.53,0:21:52.33,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to have a \Nheroine role ready for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I an 'M'?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.88,0:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A masochist. I kind of like only \Nencouraging each other through texts—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I sort of enjoy it when Azuki scolds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She got upset, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though I'm crazy about her,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still okay with not seeing her.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.94,0:22:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.44,0:22:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Azuki is crazy about you too,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.27,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so she must think the same way, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.94,0:22:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.49,0:22:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you're more of an 'N'.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An 'N'?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.60,0:22:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 'N' for narcissist.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.38,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have too many syllables in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:46.97,TLNote,,0,0,0,,Note: In Japanese, "Narcissist" is often pronounced, as just "Narsist."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm saying it right.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
