Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.56,0:24:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.97,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcement!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided on my dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.93,0:24:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.59,0:24:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Wall and Kiss.
